
AndroidTV real time Screen Streaming

DEP
    android ndk
    https://developer.android.com/ndk/downloads/index.html?hl=zh-cn
    https://dl.google.com/android/repository/android-ndk-r15b-linux-x86_64.zip

cmake >= 3.7
    build cmake 
        yum groupinstall 'Development Tools'

----
Prepare
    git submodule init
    git submodule update
    cd minicap
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

----
Build
./build.sh
结果会拷贝到bin目录中

Run
1.常规情况，
启动
sh cap1.sh rtmp://120.76.76.162/live/mzya 1080 1920  >log 2>log
停止
sh cap2.sh stop
2.androidTV在播放video



